### Web Scraping Disclaimer
This software is designed for personal use to track job applications. Users are responsible for:
- Complying with website terms of service
- Respecting rate limits and robots.txt files
- Using scraped data in accordance with applicable laws
- Not violating any platform's terms of use

### Data Privacy
- All job data is stored locally
- No personal data is transmitted to external services (except Ollama for AI features)
- Users are responsible for securing their own data

